*California<ref>{{Cite web|url= http://www.mbc.ca.gov/applicant/schools_unapproved.html|title=Medical Board of California – International Medical Schools Disapproved by the State of California|work=mbc.ca.gov|accessdate=8 September 2011}}</ref>
*[[Indiana]]<ref>{{Cite web |url= http://www.in.gov/pla/2799.htm|title=PLA: Approved/Disapproved Foreign Medical Schools|work=in.gov|accessdate=8 September 2011}}</ref>
*[[Kansas]]<ref>http://www.ksbha.org/medicalschoolsapprovedunapproved.html</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Oral surgeons bite at offshore MD degree|url=http://www.ama-assn.org/amednews/2004/10/18/prl21018.htm|publisher=AMA|accessdate=20 August 2012}}</ref>
*[[North Dakota]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ndbomex.com/DisapprovedMedSchools.pdf |title=North Dakota Board of Medical Examiners – Disapproved Medical Schools |date=23 June 2008 |work=ndbomex.com |format=PDF |accessdate=8 September 2011}}</ref>
*Texas<ref>{{cite web | last = Texas Higher Education Coordinating Board | title = Institutions Whose Degrees are Illegal to Use in Texas | url = http://www.thecb.state.tx.us/AAR/PrivateInstitutions/NoTX.cfm | accessdate =8 September 2011}}</ref>

